<h1> Creating Your Tremelo Account </h1>

<h4> Registering </h4>
Click on the Register button from the Home Page, and you will be directed to the register page.
Fill out every field with a red star. Once you hit "sign up", you will be automatically logged in and redirected to your Profile.

<h4> Customizing your account </h4>
<strong> About Me </strong><br>
